  "instructions": [
    "heat a raclette grill or grill pan to medium heat.",
    "cut the chinese cabbage in half lengthwise and steam it for 5 minutes, or until slightly tender.",
    "in a bowl, mix together the ricotta cheese, almond flour, olive oil, cinnamon, salt, and black pepper.",
    "add the steamed cabbage to the bowl and mix until the leaves are evenly coated with the cheese mixture.",
    "add the water and mix until the mixture is smooth and crumbly.",
    "divide the mixture into 4 equal parts and shape each part into a rough log.",
    "roll each log tightly in a large leaf and serve immediately.",
    "+if using sesame seeds, sprinkle them on top of each wrap for added crunch."
  ],
